item.title: Welcome
item.description: Hello World! My name is Donovan. I’m 25, residing in Tampa, Florida seeking opportunities in Software Development. I have been learning Java from this Udemy class, and doing work with Launchcode.tv This site is Powered by Hugo, a static website generator similar to Jekyll, but powered by GO, not Ruby. This is my site. I’ll blog, retheme, muse, or whatever here. You can track that progress on github
